snippet: James Udall, 61, the younger brother of Senator Mark Udall of Colorado was found dead on Wednesday in a remote Wyoming mountain range.
abstract: James Udall, younger brother of Sen Mark Udall, who has been missing for more than a week, is found dead in a remote Wyoming mountain range; no foul play is suspected.
lead_paragraph: James Udall, 61, the younger brother of Senator Mark Udall of Colorado was found dead on Wednesday in a remote Wyoming mountain range.

headline.main: Senator’s Brother Found Dead in Wyoming
